    <item>
      <title>马克龙在法国移民制度改革上犹豫不决，冒着经济命脉的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/macron-falters-reforming-france-s-migration-system-risking-an-economic-lifeline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿兰·方丹 (Alain Fontaine) 在卢浮宫附近的小酒馆里供应勃艮第牛颊肉，他依靠的是——就像许多巴黎餐馆老板一样——关于移民工人的劳动。经过四年的表格填写，本月他的一位厨师获得了居住证，标志着他克服了该国繁文缛节的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/macron-falters-reforming-france-s-migration-system-risking-an-economic-lifeline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国空手而归后，乌克兰在欧盟面临严峻考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eu-summit-ukraine-support-faces-crucial-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理维克托·欧尔班将决定欧盟领导人峰会的结果——有可能使其失败，并凸显对乌克兰的支持正在崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/eu-summit-ukraine-support-faces-crucial-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国、意大利和日本签署条约正式确定喷气式战斗机计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/uk-italy-and-japan-sign-treaty-to-formalize-stealth-jet-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国、意大利和日本周四在东京签署了一项条约，具体化了他们开发隐形战斗机的联合计划，因为两国希望在来自自信的中国等国家的威胁下加强安全关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/uk-italy-and-japan-sign-treaty-to-formalize-stealth-jet-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:09:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本岸田将改组内阁以继续掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-s-kishida-to-reshuffle-cabinet-in-bid-to-stay-in-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄将于周四改组内阁，以遏制威胁其苦苦挣扎的政府未来的资金丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/japan-s-kishida-to-reshuffle-cabinet-in-bid-to-stay-in-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 00:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国正在与盟友合作阻止胡塞武装红海袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/us-is-working-with-allies-to-stop-red-sea-attacks-pentagon-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在与盟国合作，建立多国努力，保护通过红海的船只，以阻止胡塞武装分子的袭击激增，这种袭击引发了人们对通过世界最重要水道之一的商业贸易的不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/us-is-working-with-allies-to-stop-red-sea-attacks-pentagon-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在解决工作签证混乱问题上迈出了重要一步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/south-africa-takes-major-step-toward-fixing-work-visa-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，南非内政部长签署了对工作许可法规的修改计划，旨在解决令该国最大投资者感到沮丧并加剧技能危机的官僚主义困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/south-africa-takes-major-step-toward-fixing-work-visa-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:25:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Eskom 要求政府入股该公司以减轻债务负担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eskom-said-to-seek-equity-swap-for-portion-of-its-bailout-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非负债累累的国家电力公司 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 告诉投资者，它已要求国家财政部将 160 亿兰特（8.4 亿美元）的救助资金转换为股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/eskom-said-to-seek-equity-swap-for-portion-of-its-bailout-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 17:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
